    %h1 About Shaine Hatch
    %p.portrait= image_tag "template/portrait.png", :alt => "Shaine Hatch"
    %p Shaine is a web developer based in gorgeous Salt Lake City, UT. He fancies himself a designer of websites and brand identity (but is still questing to find solid evidence to support that claim). His love for good coffee, good tea, and good beer is dwarfed by his love of the annual Burning Man festival (during which his hair usually turns orange). Shaine is one-half of the freelancing duo, Fadelight.
    %p His development workflow utilizes awesome software such as vim, tmux, zsh, and git; his configurations can be found over at his GitHub account  He is a skilled front- and back-end developer and relies on frameworks such as PHP Yii, Ruby on Rails, and Backbone.js to make great things. He is a developer/tech specialist for Digital Trike. Download his résumé here.

